videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland hits the corner 3-pointer and goes coast-to-coast for the layup midway through the first half.
videos.headline: Cumberland does it all for Cincinnati

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jacob Evans gets the block from behind on Houston's Devin Davis.
videos.headline: Evans swats away layup attempt

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jacob Evans soars in for the dunk after Kevin Johnson misses the layup just before halftime.
videos.headline: Evans flies in for putback dunk

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland knocks down the 3-pointer from the corner to help extend the lead for the Bearcats.
videos.headline: Cumberland drains the 3 to pad lead

videos.description: Cincinnati's Troy Caupain talks about his mother's influence on his play on and off the court.
videos.headline: Caupain discusses mother's influence on his game
